overview: As Russia's most infamous cat burglar, Missa wasn't used to getting caught. So after she was found trying to steal from a rich oligarch's billion-dollar mansion, she had to think fast.  It was a balmy morning in paradise that day, but it wasn't just the weather that was hot and wet. Fresh from a yoga session among the wild fronds, Emma Mae slinked onto her secluded hideaway's patio, piercing the humid air with electric blue eyes and nipples as hard as pearls.  Sweet strawberry-blonde Roberta Berti woke in a mood to tease, lying down gently on her plush bed, her fiery hair and taught, tan skin spreading out seductively against a pure white canvas of sheets.  What's going through Carmen Caliente's head as she lays back on her sofa for a bit of solo play?  Excited to try on her new bikini, Maria headed out by her pool to enjoy the feel of a summer breeze licking at her body.
title: Me, Myself & I 10
